This is the README file for IO::Statistics, a module for transparent io
statistics.

* Installation

IO::Statistics uses the stanard perl module install process:

% perl Makefile.PL
% make
# make install

* Latest version

The latest VCP-Source-cvsbk could be found on cpan or at:
http://svn.clkao.org/svnweb/member/browse/clkao/modules/IO-Statistics/

